---
// Services bileşeni
---

<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-dark">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary mb-6">
          Hizmet <span class="text-primary">Alanlarımız</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Uzmanlık alanlarımızda kapsamlı hukuki danışmanlık ve dava takibi hizmetleri sunuyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Ticaret Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Ticaret Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            Şirket kuruluşu, ticari sözleşmeler, marka ve patent hukuku, ticari uyuşmazlıklar ve daha fazlası.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• Şirket kuruluşu ve yapılandırma</li>
            <li>• Ticari sözleşme hazırlama</li>
            <li>• Marka ve patent koruması</li>
            <li>• Ticari uyuşmazlık çözümü</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- İş Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2-2v2m8 0V6a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2V6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">İş Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            İş sözleşmeleri, işçi-işveren uyuşmazlıkları, iş güvenliği ve sosyal güvenlik konuları.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• İş sözleşmesi hazırlama</li>
            <li>• İşçi-işveren uyuşmazlıkları</li>
            <li>• İş güvenliği danışmanlığı</li>
            <li>• Sosyal güvenlik hukuku</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Gayrimenkul Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Gayrimenkul Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            Tapu işlemleri, kat karşılığı inşaat sözleşmeleri, kentsel dönüşüm ve imar hukuku.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• Tapu işlemleri ve danışmanlık</li>
            <li>• Kat karşılığı inşaat sözleşmeleri</li>
            <li>• Kentsel dönüşüm hukuku</li>
            <li>• İmar ve yapı hukuku</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Ceza Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Ceza Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            Ceza davalarında savunma, şikayet dilekçesi hazırlama ve ceza hukuku danışmanlığı.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• Ceza davalarında savunma</li>
            <li>• Şikayet dilekçesi hazırlama</li>
            <li>• Ceza hukuku danışmanlığı</li>
            <li>• Adli yardım başvuruları</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Aile Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">Aile Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            Boşanma davaları, nafaka, velayet, mal paylaşımı ve aile hukuku danışmanlığı.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• Boşanma davaları</li>
            <li>• Nafaka ve velayet işlemleri</li>
            <li>• Mal paylaşımı davaları</li>
            <li>• Aile hukuku danışmanlığı</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- İcra ve İflas Hukuku -->
        <div class="group bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-dark-light/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-gradient-to-br group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-3">İcra ve İflas Hukuku</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 mb-4">
            İcra takipleri, iflas davaları, haciz işlemleri ve alacak tahsili konularında hizmet.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-secondary/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• İcra takipleri</li>
            <li>• İflas davaları</li>
            <li>• Haciz işlemleri</li>
            <li>• Alacak tahsili</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-primary-light/10 border border-primary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-4">
            Hukuki Sorunlarınız İçin Profesyonel Çözüm
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Uzman ekibimizle hukuki sorunlarınızı çözmek için buradayız. 
            Ücretsiz ön görüşme için hemen iletişime geçin.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="#contact" 
              class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light hover:from-primary-light hover:to-primary text-dark font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/25 transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              Ücretsiz Danışmanlık
            </a>
            <a 
              href="tel:03129550550" 
              class="border-2 border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-dark font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300"
            >
              Hemen Ara
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 